==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cloud-built
<hw>Cloud"-built</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Built of, or in,
the clouds; airy; unsubstantial; imaginary.</def>
<rj><au>Cowper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>So vanished my <qex>cloud-built</qex> palace.</q>
<rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cloud-burst</ent>⟦br⟧
